data.description: Charming bungalow situated in the highly desirable Milner Crest neighborhood. This residence boasts numerous recent improvements, such as new siding (completion expected by next month), modern windows, an upgraded bathroom, and fresh carpeting. The home exudes character with its metal kitchen cabinets and a cast iron farmhouse sink. The sizable backyard is fenced and includes a storage shed. Don't miss out ? reach out to your real estate agent now to arrange a viewing!
